{"id": 225019072, "title": "Greece Getting Wego Travel App, Artificial Intelligence to Guide Tourists", "text": "Greece\u2019s National Tourism Organization (GNTO) is teaming with the travel app Wego from Singapore and Dubai to make finding flights and accommodations and tourism sites easier for visitors \u2013 along with a coming Artificial Intelligence model. Wego officials said the partnership \u201cinvites travelers to immerse themselves in Greece\u2019s breathtaking landscapes, rich history, and exquisite cuisine, promising an unforgettable Mediterranean adventure.\u201d It added that a campaign as Greece expects another successive record-breaking year \u201cwill feature an array of activities, and tailored travel experiences designed to capture the essence of Greece\u2019s charm and allure,\u201d said Breaking News Travel. Travelers will have access to the advanced search and booking features on Wego\u2019s platform to find deals while Digital Governance Minister Dimitris Papastergiou said that an AI app \u2013 through the Tourism Ministry \u2013 will be presented on June 3. Mamoun Hmedan, Chief Business Officer of Wego, said, \u201cGreece offers an unparalleled mix of history, culture, and natural beauty, making it a top choice for summer travel. Through this partnership, we aim to inspire and facilitate memorable travel experiences for our users and drive more visitations.\u201d GNTO Secretary-General Dimitris Fragakis said, \u201cWe are joining forces with Wego to showcase how with easy flight connectivity, Greece is an accessible paradise, perfect for creating unforgettable memories.\u201d", "summary": "<p>Greece\u2019s National Tourism Organization (GNTO) is teaming with the travel app Wego from Singapore and Dubai to make finding flights&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https://www.thenationalherald.com/greece-getting-wego-travel-app-artificial-intelligence-to-guide-tourists/\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Greece Getting Wego Travel App, Artificial Intelligence to Guide Tourists</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.thenationalherald.com/greece-getting-wego-travel-app-artificial-intelligence-to-guide-tourists/\">Greece Getting Wego Travel App, Artificial Intelligence to Guide Tourists</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.thenationalherald.com\">The National Herald</a>.</p>", "url": "https://www.thenationalherald.com/greece-getting-wego-travel-app-artificial-intelligence-to-guide-tourists/", "image": "https://www.thenationalherald.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/AP24107359298906-scaled.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-29 12:52:08", "author": "Achilleas Kouremenos", "authors": ["Achilleas Kouremenos"], "language": "en", "source_country": "us", "sentiment": 1.0}